1. Ja sam *zauzeta* sutra ujutru. (I am *busy* tomorrow morning.)
2. Oni su *zauzeti* ovog vikenda. (They are *busy* this weekend.)
3. Molim te da ne zoveš jer sam *zauzet*. (Please don't call because I am *busy*.)
4. *Zauzmi* svoje mesto, molim te. (Please *take* your seat.)
5. Moramo *zauzeti* ozbiljan stav po pitanju zaštite životne sredine. (We need to *adopt* a serious stance regarding environmental protection.)
6. Oni su *zauzeli* grad. (They *occupied* the city.)
7. Nadam se da ćemo *zauzeti* prvo mesto na takmičenju. (I hope we will *take* the first place in the competition.)
8. Oni su *zauzeti* planiranjem letnjeg odmora. (They are *occupied* with planning their summer vacation.)
9. Ne mogu da dođem na sastanak jer sam već *zauzet* u to vreme. (I can't come to the meeting because I am already *booked* at that time.)
10. Možeš *zauzeti* ovaj sto ako želiš. (You can *occupy* this table if you want.)